Product Description▼▲
Long ago a prophet of God hides his powers in a hold of fire and becomes a simple man living on a mountainside. When somebody discovers the key to the treasure, Ilfredo is sent to stop the thief. But a great evil and his army sleep beside the cache. Can the hero win this battle---alone? 320 pages, softcover from Living Ink.

Product Information▼▲
Format: PaperbackNumber of Pages: 320Vendor: Living InkPublication Date: 2012ISBN: 0899578624ISBN-13: 9780899578620Series: Sword of the Dragon

