5
 
Meets Expectations:




5
  
            Scott Appleton takes the storyline of The Sword of the Dragon series and brings a more powerful blow to his audience with each book!! Appleton so smoothly writes the story of his characters and their world that he has captured my heart and imagination with characters like Specter, Ilfedo, Oganna and the Warrioress! Anyone interested in taking the chance to let you imagination be enraptured by Appleton's world should pick up the series The Sword of the Dragon from book one Sword of the Six to his lastest book Key of Living Fire!


Key of Living Fire was an excellent read and everytime I picked it up to find out what was going to happen next to the characters I found when I finally put it down I'd read through several chapters!!
        














